Thanks for downloading the EBU MXF Toolkit.s

>> sh autogen.sh
>> ./configure
>> make

if you need to add some pathes to your pkgconfig...
>> sh autogen.sh
>> ./configure PKG_CONFIG_PATH=/Path/to/pkgconfig
>> make

or quicker from src directory

>> c++ -std=c++11 *.cpp -o MXFTools `pkg-config --libs --cflags gtkmm-3.0 gdkmm-3.0 gstreamermm-0.10 xerces-c libMXF-1.0 libMXF++-1.0 bmx-0.1 ebu-mxfsdk-1.0` -W -Wall

or

>> g++ -std=c++11 *.cpp -o MXFTools `pkg-config --libs --cflags gtkmm-3.0 gdkmm-3.0 gstreamermm-0.10 xerces-c libMXF-1.0 libMXF++-1.0 bmx-0.1 ebu-mxfsdk-1.0` -W -Wall
